---
// Custom Hero landing page – bypasses Starlight routing
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="A common shape for agents that live alongside people." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Bub" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="A common shape for agents that live alongside people." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://bub.build" />
    <title>Bub — A common shape for agents that live alongside people.</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      :root {
        --accent: #4f7eff;
        --accent-soft: rgba(79, 126, 255, 0.12);
        --bg: #0d0f1a;
        --surface: #1a1d2e;
        --surface-2: #252840;
        --text: #e8eaf6;
        --text-muted: #888b99;
        --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        --radius: 10px;
        --font: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        --font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Code", ui-monospace, monospace;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
        :root {
          --bg: #f6f7fb;
          --surface: #ffffff;
          --surface-2: #eef0f9;
          --text: #0d0f1a;
          --text-muted: #545766;
          --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
      }

      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        font-family: var(--font);
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* ── Nav ── */
      nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 100;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        height: 60px;
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 80%, transparent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .nav-logo {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        list-style: none;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

      .nav-links .btn-nav {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fff !important;
        padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
      }

      .nav-links .btn-nav:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

      /* ── Hero ── */
      .hero {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .hero-code { display: none; }
      }

      .hero-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        border: 1px solid rgba(79,126,255,0.25);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.85rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.15;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .hero-title span { color: var(--accent); }

      .hero-sub {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        max-width: 480px;
      }

      .hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fff;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: var(--surface-2);
        color: var(--text);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--surface); transform: translateY(-1px); }

      /* Code block */
      .hero-code {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      }

      .code-topbar {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        background: var(--surface-2);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
      .dot-r { background: #ff5f57; }
      .dot-y { background: #febc2e; }
      .dot-g { background: #28c840; }

      .code-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: auto; font-family: var(--font-mono); }

      pre {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        overflow-x: auto;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .kw  { color: #c792ea; }
      .fn  { color: #82aaff; }
      .dec { color: #ffcb6b; }
      .str { color: #c3e88d; }
      .cm  { color: var(--text-muted); }
      .cls { color: #f78c6c; }

      /* ── Pipeline ── */
      .pipeline-section {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .section-sub {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 540px;
        margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .pipeline {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }

      .pipe-step {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.25rem;
      }

      .pipe-box {
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        border: 1px solid rgba(79,126,255,0.3);
        color: var(--accent);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-weight: 600;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .pipe-arrow {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        padding: 0 0.3rem;
        line-height: 2.2;
      }

      .pipeline-caption {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
      }

      /* ── Features ── */
      .features-section {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
      }

      .features-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

      .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }

      .feature-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      }

      .feature-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(79,126,255,0.35);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .feature-icon {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .feature-title {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .feature-desc {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      /* ── Install CTA ── */
      .install-section {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .install-box {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
      }

      .install-title {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .install-sub {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .install-cmd {
        background: var(--surface-2);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .install-cmd .prompt { color: var(--accent); user-select: none; }

      .install-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      /* ── Footer ── */
      footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1.5rem clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
      }

      footer a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- ── Navigation ── -->
    <nav>
      <a class="nav-logo" href="/">bub</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/en/">Docs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/architecture/">Architecture</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/extension-guide/">Extend</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/bubbuild/bub">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/" class="btn-nav">Get Started →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="6"/></svg>
          Group-chat native · Hook-first · Tape context
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          A common shape for agents that live alongside
          <span>people.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Bub is a hook-first agent framework built for real collaboration —
          not demos. One pipeline. Every channel. Extensible at every stage.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/">Get Started →</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://github.com/bubbuild/bub">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/></svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-code" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="code-topbar">
          <span class="dot dot-r"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-y"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-g"></span>
          <span class="code-label">plugin.py</span>
        </div>
        <pre><code><span class="kw">from</span> bub <span class="kw">import</span> hookimpl
<span class="kw">from</span> republic <span class="kw">import</span> AsyncStreamEvents, StreamEvent

<span class="cm"># Override any stage of the pipeline.</span>
<span class="cm"># Builtins are just default plugins.</span>

<span class="kw">class</span> <span class="cls">EchoPlugin</span>:
    <span class="dec">@hookimpl</span>
    <span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">build_prompt</span>(self, message, session_id, state):
        <span class="kw">return</span> <span class="str">f"[echo] {message['content']}"</span>

    <span class="dec">@hookimpl</span>
    <span class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">run_model_stream</span>(self, prompt, ...):
        <span class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">_iter</span>():
            <span class="kw">yield</span> StreamEvent(<span class="str">"text"</span>, {<span class="str">"delta"</span>: prompt})
        <span class="kw">return</span> AsyncStreamEvents(_iter())</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Pipeline ── -->
    <section class="pipeline-section">
      <p class="section-label">Turn Lifecycle</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">One pipeline. Every channel.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Every inbound message passes through the same hook-driven pipeline —
        CLI, Telegram, or any channel you add.
      </p>
      <div class="pipeline">
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">resolve_session</span></div>
        <span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">load_state</span></div>
        <span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">build_prompt</span></div>
        <span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">run_model_stream</span></div>
        <span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">render_outbound</span></div>
        <span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="pipe-step"><span class="pipe-box">dispatch_outbound</span></div>
      </div>
      <p class="pipeline-caption">Each stage is a pluggy hook. Override any of them.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Features ── -->
    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="features-header">
        <p class="section-label">Why Bub</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Built for real teams, not demos</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">
          Bub grew up in multi-person group chats where single-user assumptions
          break immediately. These constraints shaped everything.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔌</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Hook-First Architecture</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            The turn pipeline <em>is</em> hooks. Builtins are ordinary plugins — no magic,
            no special cases. Override <code>build_prompt</code>, <code>run_model_stream</code>,
            or <code>render_outbound</code> simply by registering your own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📼</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Tape-Based Context</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            History is append-only facts. Context is assembled on demand —
            not accumulated, not compressed into lossy summaries.
            Your working set is always current.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Channel-Agnostic Pipeline</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            CLI and Telegram share the same <code>process_inbound()</code> path.
            Hooks don't know which channel they're in. Adding a new channel is
            just implementing one interface.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Skills as Documents</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            Skills are <code>SKILL.md</code> files with validated frontmatter, not
            code modules with magic registration. Ship them in packages.
            Override them per-workspace or per-user.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🧩</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">~200-Line Core</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            The core is intentionally small. Builtins are default plugins you can
            replace. No privileged internal path. Every default is an example
            of how to write a plugin.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Socialized Evaluation</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            Humans and agents share the same operator model. Execution is visible,
            handoff is safe, and continuation is predictable — even when multiple
            people and agents are working in the same context.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔧</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Plugin Ecosystem</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            External plugins load via Python entry-points. Later-registered plugins
            run first. Any builtin behavior can be overridden — or wrapped —
            without forking the core.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Multi-Channel Gateway</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">
            <code>bub gateway</code> starts a channel listener for Telegram and any
            adapter you add. The same skills, the same context, the same hooks —
            across every surface.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Install CTA ── -->
    <section class="install-section">
      <div class="install-box">
        <h2 class="install-title">Get started in seconds</h2>
        <p class="install-sub">Install from PyPI, configure a model key, and start building.</p>
        <div class="install-cmd">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span>pip install bub</span>
        </div>
        <div class="install-links">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/">Read the Docs →</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://github.com/bubbuild/bub">View on GitHub</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://pypi.org/project/bub">PyPI</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Footer ── -->
    <footer>
      <p>
        Copyright &copy; 2026 <a href="https://github.com/bubbuild">Bub Build</a> contributors.
        Licensed under <a href="https://github.com/bubbuild/bub/blob/main/LICENSE">Apache-2.0</a>.
      </p>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
